SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT PRD_LIN, EFM, MTOCD, MTONAM, PLN_SEQ, PLN_SFX, COL_CD, EF_TYP, SHA_NO FROM PRD005 WHERE PLN_DAT BETWEEN ':1' AND ':2' and PRD_LIN = ':3' ORDER BY PRD_LIN, EFM DESC, PLN_SEQ, PLN_SFX, SHA_NO
SELECT MTOCD, MTONAM, COUNT(*) FROM PRD005 WHERE PLN_DAT = ':1' AND PRD_LIN = ':2' AND EFM = ':3' GROUP BY MTOCD, MTONAM ORDER BY MTOCD
